hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm in my first year at university coromed.us Opening the new season’s International Piano Series at the Southbank, Levit confirmed all previous impressions as one of the most important pianists to have emerged in recent years. His place on the BBC New Generation Artists scheme is a reminder that he is only in his mid twenties, yet already he plays with the maturity of a great artist and looks set to be one of this century’s big names.
